      '**Konsistenz-Check**: H1 â€” Dashboard `text-[18px] leading-[1.12] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] truncate` â‰، Vehicle-Detail post-V4.7.08. Tab-Pille â€” Dashboard-Fleet-Status `text-[12px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.003em]` â‰، Vehicle-Detail-Tabs post-V4.7.08. Meta-Label â€” Dashboard-Insights-Tile `text-[10.5px] font-semibold` â‰، Connection-Badge-Sub-Label post-V4.7.08.',
      '**Nicht berأ¼hrt**: License-/Station-/Fuel-Info-Pillen (waren bereits `sq-section-label` + `text-[12px] font-semibold tabular-nums` â€” matcht Dashboard-Pattern). `sq-chip` Status-/Cleaning-/Health-Pillen (Token-basiert, identisch in beiden Views). Page-Body unter den Tabs (Trips-Filter-Bar, Overview-Live-Map-Card, Vehicle-Insights-Card, Health-Errors-View) â€” separates Komponenten-Scope, hier nicht im Lieferumfang.',
