      'VERIFIED: Mercedes-Trip b263cdb8 wurde via verify-intra-trip-gap-split.ts retroaktiv gesplittet. Vorher: 1 Trip (15:50â†’16:04, 2.0km, 13.96min, endMode=NO_ACTIVITY_TIMEOUT, 75 Waypoints). Nachher: 2 Trips â€” b263cdb8 (15:50â†’15:53:44, 1.03km, 3.38min, endMode=MID_TRIP_GAP_SPLIT, 30 Waypoints) + cc18ab03 (15:57:07â†’16:04, 1.11km, 7.19min, startMode=MID_TRIP_GAP_SPLIT, endMode=INTRA_TRIP_GAP_SPLIT_REPAIR, isRepaired=true, 45 Waypoints). Gap=203s Drift=4m. TripRepair-Row status=APPLIED, Enrichment fأ¼r cc18ab03 enqueued',
      'backend/src/modules/vehicle-intelligence/trips/decision/trip-decision.engine.ts (splitTripAtGap), decision/decision.types.ts (SplitTripAtGapParams, SplitTripAtGapResult), trip-detection.types.ts (neue Modes), reconciliation/reconciliation.types.ts (REPAIR_TYPES.INTRA_TRIP_GAP_SPLIT), reconciliation/trip-reconciliation.service.ts (repairIntraTripGapSplits + splitCompletedTripRecursively + findWaypointGapForSplit + haversineMeters), trip-detection-orchestration.service.ts (mid-trip gap-Branch in processActiveTick + findMidTripGap + computeMidGapPositionDrift), config/worker.config.ts (3 neue Keys)',
