      'backend/prisma/schema.prisma + migrations/20260417160000_add_mqtt_only_hm_sync_status/migration.sql â€” HmSyncStatus enum extended with MQTT_ONLY; backend/scripts/apply-mqtt-only-enum.ts applied the ALTER TYPE directly because an older index-concurrent migration blocks migrate deploy',
      'backend/src/modules/high-mobility/high-mobility-health-fetch.service.ts â€” on first 404 from /v1/vehicles/{ref}/command the vehicle is flipped to streamingState=CONFIGURED (was left at NOT_CONFIGURED indefinitely)',
      'backend/src/workers/schedulers/hm-health-polling.scheduler.ts â€” REST polling suppression filter now skips both CONNECTED and CONFIGURED streamingStates (was: CONNECTED only)',
      'backend/scripts/cleanup-stale-hm-error-messages.ts â€” one-off maintenance script that cleared stale MQTT_ONLY and OAuth network leftover strings in hmSignalGroupState.lastErrorMessage where lastErrorAt was null',
